Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you able to control\Nthe Nine-Tails Chakra okay, Tenzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no problems so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, please call me Yamato,\Nnot Tenzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It cut quite a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!\NAnd mine still hasn't cut at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm much better than you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're me, I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...\NThat me over there's pretty good...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Say! Say!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got something I want to ask you,\NKakashi Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone in the Leaf\Nwho has the wind property?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You going to ask about the trick to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you could say\Nthere's a person...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right about now\Nhe's probably playing shogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I lost again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Our next end-of-mission party's\Non you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuma Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As it happens,\Nthere's something I want to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:43.24,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(1027,591)}Writhe\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The trick to the wind\NChange in Chakra Nature, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're doing Chakra\NChange in Chakra Nature training?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to have a sense\Nfor that kind of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I came here\Nto ask Asuma Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the same wind\NChakra property as me, right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd have\Nthe wind Chakra property, Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is indeed a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuma Sensei, please teach me\Nthe trick to it...right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I could think about it if you'd pay\Nthe barbeque bill
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,for Team Asuma's\Nnext end-of-mission party...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's it...\N{\i1}Just enough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll lose everything I've got, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice.\NIt's for my training!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! It's a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my Chakra Blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This blade is made from\Na special metal
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that absorbs\Nthe owner's Chakra property.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Try pouring your Chakra into the blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My Chakra...kind of comes out\Ndifferent than yours, Asuma Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind Change in Chakra Nature\Nsplits Chakra in two
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and grinds them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Grinds them together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you build up\Nthe two Chakra as if steadily honing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As if steadily ...honing them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The trick is steady ...and sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... um... I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we've got\NNinja Tools to start with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is there a point to this wind\NChange in Chakra Nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be quicker just to cut with\Nsomething that cuts right from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And is there a point...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to pouring cutting Chakra into\Na weapon that already cuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll show you whether\Nor not there's a point to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll try throwing these Chakra Blades\Ntoward that tree at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two--!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It went all the way through...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}not just the tree but into that\N{\i1}really hard rock and got lodged inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous,\Nso I held back just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've gone right through\Nthe rock if I'd gone all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The quality of the blade\Nwill determine the result
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in the case of Ninja of the same level\Ngetting into a serious battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind Property has the most attack \N power in close to medium-range battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There really aren't that many... wind types.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on by if there's ever\Nanything else you want to ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll have to pay\Nfor the barbeque.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was a Shadow Clone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He forgot that we've got\NChoji on our team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's harsh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can he really create something\Nlike a new Jutsu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,before the Akatsuki start moving\Ninto high gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be best to keep\NNaruto hidden somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,before making contact with the Akatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's up to the Fifth Hokage to decide...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! So that's how to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's do it!\N- Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It appears he found out the trick\N{\i1}to it from Asuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's already doing a good job
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of applying the attributes of\N{\i1}his Shadow Clones, that Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When a friend is putting extra effort\Ninto work or a hobby,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you should casually bring them\Nsome refreshment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got more problems...\Nthan extra effort...
Comment: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a first for you, going with a\N climbing silver right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take it nice and slow.\NWe've got the time, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an advance guard for\Nbreaking through the enemy's defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you have to be able\Nto make moves like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you didn't like moves like that.\NJust like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrifice is required in order to protect\Nthe king when your opponent is skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I just now started to understand\Nthe importance of the "king."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... The game is over if\Nyou get your king taken in Shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:10:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to liken the Hidden Leaf Shinobi\Nto a Shogi piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru...\NIn the end, you would be a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Although weak in strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,a knight can advance\Nby jumping over pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This unique movement resembles\Nyour flexible thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what would you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nothing.\NI'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A sacrificial piece...huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... do you know who the "king" is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hokage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought until just recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You dodge well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My attack speed is the slowest\Nin the Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't hit anything, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...\NI knew you guys were Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the Two-Tailed Jinchuriki.\NYou'll die if you get careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that, Kakuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like her to kill me anyway.
Comment: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! We'll go ahead and\Nhave you accumulate experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruminate in your head on\Nthe training and break the Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right!\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can manage this...\NI'll be able to do it soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The drawback is that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,mental fatigue is accumulated\Nalong with the experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But...I'm almost there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a short break, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to be taking it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay, Kakashi Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Multi Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What...? Oh! Hey...\NJust a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...That's incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really working hard, Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, I guess with his stamina, {\i1}he'll be fine.
Comment: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure was young...\Nback then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good work...\N{\i1}on the Feudal Lord escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I protected the king, the Feudal Lord\N{\i1}just as you told me to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why don't you even attempt\N{\i1}to acknowledge me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}King...huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How about acknowledging me\N{\i1}at least a little bit, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}how difficult and important a battle\N{\i1}to protect the king is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:16:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand that people died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But sacrifice comes with\N{\i1}a Shinobi mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can't possibly\N{\i1}understand now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the true significance of\N{\i1}protecting the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just don't want to\N{\i1}acknowledge me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I get the feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of understand what\Nyou were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I left the Hidden Leaf...\Nand just did whatever I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no regrets, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I feel like it wasn't so bad\Nbeing born into the Sarutobi Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You properly fulfilled your duty\Nas leader of the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a cool dad...
Comment: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! Am I awesome or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I'll master a new Jutsu just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No...You're making fast progress\Nbecause of this training approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to my amazing idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also thanks quite a bit to me,\NKakashi Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,\NI'm ready to get right to my next training...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well! You can do it because it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamato, let's take a short break\Nwhile we're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Naruto be okay...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be fine if he rests a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this kid's really something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...? What is it, Sakura...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Tsunade wants to see you...
Comment: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Attacks by what is suspected to be\N{\i1}the same two-man Shinobi team
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in seven locations in five\N{\i1}neighboring lands have been verified.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although they have not yet succeeded\N{\i1}in invading the Land of Fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}judging from their line of action,\N{\i1}it's only a matter of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Tsunade?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So the Akatsuki Organization\N{\i1}has gone into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Before doing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I must pray to my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always\Nsuch a pain in the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pain\Nin the neck for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But the commandments are strict,\Nso I have no choice, do I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably think\Nyou've got me cornered...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I lured you guys here, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I know you are with the Akatsuki,\N I cannot let you escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man...\NWe're trapped, Kakuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.\NActually, this is favorable for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of Yugito Ni 'i\Nof the Hidden Clouds...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:20:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with that,\N"I'll kill you," stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When people show me all\Nthat enthusiasm and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I start to get irritated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I'm irritated,\NI become enraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I become enraged...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Hidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know,\Nwhen I become enraged,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I start feeling like,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"I don't care about our objective.\NI just want to smash everything."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, Hidan.\NThe objective is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This mission doesn't go along\Nwith my religion in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The motto of the Jashin religion\Nis mass slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving people alive goes\Nagainst the commandments.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,From the outset, I'm not inclined\Nto take part in a mission
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that breaks\Nthe commandments.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not look it,\Nbut I'm quite devout!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.11,0:21:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So not being able to kill\Nis a pain in the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So how about we settle this\Nby talking things over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking things over, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's up with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you\Njust come quietly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.43,0:22:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? Looks like that's a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.31,0:22:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.11,0:22:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with this Jinchuriki?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's totally morphed into a Tailed Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.16,0:23:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cats have sensitive tongues\Nfor hot stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the Two-Tails monster cat\Nknown as the wraith...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.27,0:23:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm a rat in a cage, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.94,0:23:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not amusing...
Comment: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.21,0:23:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I read the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it look like Naruto will be able\Nto learn a new Jutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.30,0:23:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:23:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.82,0:24:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.54,0:24:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But he can probably do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.83,0:24:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That new training approach\Nis yielding results, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And more importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.26,0:24:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a clear objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.88,0:24:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been thirty minutes.\NAren't you done yet, Hidan?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.66,0:25:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NDon't interfere with the ritual!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.10,0:25:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.06,0:25:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you skip some of that perverse praying\Nyou do each and every time?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.82,0:25:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get right to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.84,0:25:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a pain in the neck for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.98,0:25:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have no choice\Nbut to follow the commandments.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.53,0:25:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do you mean by skip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.58,0:25:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's blasphemy against God!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.62,0:25:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more to go for our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.38,0:25:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.38,0:25:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is the Land of Fire.
